## ⚡ CHEAT SHEET — Câu Hỏi Nhanh Có Thể Bị Hỏi

| Câu hỏi | Key Points |
|---|---|
| ROS 1 vs ROS 2? | ROS2: DDS middleware, real-time capable, security, multi-robot native |
| PID tuning thế nào? | Ziegler-Nichols hoặc manual tune: P → ổn định, I → steady-state error, D → giảm overshoot |
| Sim-to-Real gap? | Domain randomization, system identification, progressive transfer |
| Python vs C++ cho robotics? | Python: prototyping + ML. C++: low-latency control loop, embedded |
| Docker vs VM? | Docker: lightweight, share kernel, fast startup. VM: full isolation |
| A* vs Dijkstra? | A* có heuristic → nhanh hơn cho single-target. Dijkstra tìm shortest path tới tất cả nodes |
| Overfitting trong RL? | Nhiều diverse environments, domain randomization, early stopping |
| Transformer vs RNN cho sequence? | Transformer: parallel, long-range. RNN: sequential, lighter |

